  "title": "Aether Compat: Gloves For All",
  "description": "Adds gloves for selected other mods' materials, improving parity of sets and their abilities with The Aether.",
  "body": "<center>\n  <a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/All_rights_reserved\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/assets%20license-All%20Rights%20Reserved-red.svg?style=flat-square\" alt=\"Asset license (All Rights Reserved)\"></a>\n  \n  <a href=\"https://github.com/KreloX/Gloves-For-All/blob/1.20.1/LICENSE.txt\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/code%20license-LGPL%20v3.0-green.svg?style=flat-square\" alt=\"Code license (LGPL v3.0)\"></a>\n</center>\n\n<center>\n  <a href='https://moddex.gg/mod/aether-gloves-for-all'><img src='https://moddex.gg/badges/projects/aether-gloves-for-all/rating.svg?style=devin' alt='ModDex rating'>\n  </a>\n</center>\n\n<br>\n<h2><center>🥊 About this addon 🥊</center></h2>\n  \n<p>\n  The Gloves For All addon introduces gloves variants for selected other mods' materials. \nGloves can be crafted or found the same way as their respective other pieces of armor.\nAny full set abilities now also require gloves to be equipped (unless disabled in The Aether's server config).\n</p>\n\n<p>\n  For Aether compatibility with Twilight Forest use\n  <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/umbral-skies\">Umbral Skies</a>\n</p>\n\n<h3>Includes support for the following mods:</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/caverns-and-chasms\">Caverns & Chasms</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/savage-and-ravage\">Savage & Ravage</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/oreganized\">Oreganized</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/galosphere\">Galosphere</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/addadd\">Additional Additions</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/simpleores\">SimpleOres</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/the-undergarden\">The Undergarden</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/blue-skies\">Blue Skies</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/voidscape\">Voidscape</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/the-midnight\">The Midnight</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/deeperdarker\">Deeper and Darker</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/botania\">Botania</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/create\">Create</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/redstone-arsenal\">Redstone Arsenal</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/tools-complement\">Tool's Complement</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/thermal-cultivation\">Thermal Cultivation</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/thermal-innovation\">Thermal Innovation</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/thermal-extra\">Thermal Extra</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/mekanism-tools\">Mekanism Tools</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/ice-and-fire-dragons\">Ice and Fire</a></li>\n</ul>\n\n<center>\n  <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a37bc7ff0ce5bc39482171cc41d9c1825b7ad76e.png\">\n</center>\n\n<br>\n<h2><center>☁️ Authorship notice ☁️</center></h2>\n\n<p>\n  Gloves For All is an unofficial addon developed by KreloX without involvement from The Aether Team.\n</p>\n\n<center>\n  <a href=\"https://tinyurl.com/kreloxkinetic\">\n    <img src=\"https://1drv.ms/i/c/6bf544900f9867ae/IQR3yxNMtle9S4RxniPeeGgMAVrcnQ4U65DGA1uiSdBUIbE?width=837&height=80\" width=\"837\" height=\"80\" />\n  </a>\n</center>\n",
